{"tid":1825860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(重新出post)有班大專生整左條反送中嘅小電影","createTime":"2020-01-15T15:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T18:33:50.000Z","uid":148317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb43dacb37a843a383155a09ed8f678e2ed8be7d","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已糾正為小電影</span></span></strong>上個post啊叔唔識分，對唔住各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇睇下youtube見到有條片，係光復香港，時代革命嘅小電影&lt;&lt;習慣&gt;&gt;。 雖然成條片有d位聲同剪接都有待改善。但開頭個部分做引入整得好好，現實就好似大白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中間個幕個男仔扮便衣曱甴捉手足幾逼真，但唔夠真曱甴仆街。最後出現2019年成個畫面同文宣，真係喊出黎，回憶通通出曬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然條片有d不足，但見到條片嘅簡介，原來係一班大專生去做group project整作出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到有大專生唔怕被學校打壓去交一份有政治立場嘅功課。值得一讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係睇翻個view數只係得40個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手足一齊入去睇爆佢。入去比Like，推爆佢。 一班學生為左鼓勵大家繼續行，比更多人知香港人抗爭，唔知佢哋有冇試過比學校打壓。都選擇去拍關於抗爭片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我睇到好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望手足一齊推爆，Like爆條片，報答翻班學生。<br />\n<br />\nsorry我講到1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有記住1月19大遊行<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ByfA4gE_PP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FByfA4gE_PP4&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=9ea283f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ByfA4gE_PP4</a> <br />\n<br />\n支持黃色影片界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49TUjA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49TUjA8.jpg&h=08b84390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dc7c088d540a4c12700c296ddbd09de472b7643","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"重新推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f22ce22bfb8c22528cd8b940ca10eb0151ab503","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0052a58db4eb33be5a4373d994ecd3d6ec928aa6","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"二推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c865dc4fab3ae11f673a0dbc4ed463d5653457df","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"三推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9a14eb5c09550ceee9f404172bfa0e5c85b6b7","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"四推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360497cee47ac72914542e8fc2bbd83df3ac2498","tid":1825860,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/13/160301_87afd36c751a7a4e2d629b62dc6962e6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F13%2F160301_87afd36c751a7a4e2d629b62dc6962e6.gif&h=23c3d60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望大家唔好忘記每一個曾經感動你堅持落去嘅理由"},{"pid":"376cc1fff264056f1d486298dbb56ff1b966aacd","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:01:40.000Z","msg":"五推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb972f2a1c7d4b4009eacb8cc76d36f4d5e091ad","tid":1825860,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re